<span class="voters">
<span class="user-block">知乎用户、</span><span class="user-block"><a data-tip="p$t$chen-duo-duo-10-21" href="http://www.zhihu.com/people/chen-duo-duo-10-21" class="zg-link" title="陈多多">陈多多</a>、</span><span class="user-block"><a data-tip="p$t$wang-mo-mo-51-55" href="http://www.zhihu.com/people/wang-mo-mo-51-55" class="zg-link" title="初音">初音</a></span>
