<div class="zm-item-answer-detail">
<div class="zm-item-answer-author-info">
<h3 class="zm-item-answer-author-wrap">


<a data-tip="p$t$zeroworldc" href="/people/zeroworldc">ZeroworldC</a>，<strong title="不是女汉子" class="zu-question-my-bio">不是女汉子</strong>

</h3>
<a href="javascript:;" name="collapse" class="collapse meta-item zg-right"><i class="z-icon-fold"></i>收起</a>
</div>
<div class="zm-item-vote-info " data-votecount="2">

<span class="voters">
<span class="user-block"><a data-tip="p$t$lu-a-san" href="http://www.zhihu.com/people/lu-a-san" class="zg-link" title="卢阿三">卢阿三</a>、</span><span class="user-block"><a data-tip="p$t$ddd-elena" href="http://www.zhihu.com/people/ddd-elena" class="zg-link" title="ddd elena">ddd elena</a></span>
</span>


<span>赞同</span>


</div>
<div class="zm-item-rich-text" data-resourceid="424860" data-action="/answer/content">

<div class="fixed-summary zm-editable-content clearfix">其实没那么多大道理。<br>没有自我=没有创造力，没有主见，没有自己的爱好和激情，没有持久力。<br>太过人云亦云，把自己磨的滑滑的，看上去还不错，实则黯然无光，外实中空。


</div>

